250
00:23:03,884 --> 00:23:04,885
But cool.

251
00:23:08,013 --> 00:23:09,139
- [chuckles]
- [Jason] Have fun.

252
00:23:09,139 --> 00:23:10,390
- [laughs]
- Be yourself.

253
00:23:12,184 --> 00:23:14,645
