298
00:26:41,977 --> 00:26:44,271
You said our choices create worlds.

299
00:26:46,106 --> 00:26:52,529
And so, theoretically, we simultaneously inhabited an infinite number of them.

300
00:26:56,950 --> 00:27:02,206
