- [phone ringing] [Jason] All over.

321
00:28:46,727 --> 00:28:52,024
You know, uh, Jay,
what I think is that, uh, you should eat a bag of dicks.

322
00:28:52,024 --> 00:28:56,236
And please let me
microwave them for you first, so they're nice and fucking hot for your mouth.

323
00:28:56,236 --> 00:28:58,363
Fuck you. Honestly, man.

324
00:28:58,363 --> 00:29:00,407
Ryan. Ryan, l-listen, man.

325
00:29:00,407 --> 00:29:02,534
- Ryan! I'm not fucking with you.
- [Ryan] What?

326
00:29:02,534 --> 00:29:05,787
I have not lost my mind. I swear.

327
00:29:05,787 --> 00:29:06,872
I hear you.

328
00:29:08,040 --> 00:29:10,042
