Just need answers.

358
00:31:55,499 --> 00:31:56,500
Yeah.

359
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:04,341
I know you think that I have lost my mind.

360
00:32:08,887 --> 00:32:10,347
Get some sleep.

361
00:32:52,764 --> 00:32:55,100
