- [breathing heavily]
- [phone ringing] Hello? [breathing heavily]

393
00:36:22,891 --> 00:36:23,976
[Jason] Hi.

394
00:36:24,768 --> 00:36:28,522
Oh, my God. Jason.
Are you okay? [breathes heavily]

395
00:36:29,523 --> 00:36:30,649
