453
00:43:28,984 --> 00:43:30,360
Holy fuck.

454
00:43:31,820 --> 00:43:33,822
- What?
- He did it.

455
00:43:35,324 --> 00:43:38,952
Son of a... He did it.

456
00:43:38,952 --> 00:43:40,579
[tires squealing]

457
00:43:41,705 --> 00:43:42,706
[Daniela] He did what?

458
00:43:44,249 --> 00:43:45,626
