476
00:46:25,244 --> 00:46:27,037
I'm glad you found your way to me.

477
00:46:29,248 --> 00:46:30,249
I am too.

478
00:46:36,421 --> 00:46:37,422
What's this?

479
00:46:39,716 --> 00:46:41,510
That's proof.

480
00:46:44,721 --> 00:46:45,722
